General.Name: Castile Resources Ltd
General.Description: Castile Resources Limited engages in the mineral exploration and project development activities in Australia. The company focuses on exploring for copper-gold and other base metals. It holds 100% interests in the Rover and Warumpi projects that are located in the Northern Territory. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is based in West Leederville, Australia.
